PN,31108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778767870
OL,3,CWill Rayner take the chance to seize
OL,4,CLabour leadership? She's not ruling it
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,F(I tried to ask Rayner about the
OL,8,Flatter candidate, but again, "no
OL,9,Fhypotheticals" was the response to
OL,10,FMiliband).
OL,12,FWhat was notable was that Angela
OL,13,FRayner already had a firm idea of what
OL,14,FLabour needed to do in order to win
OL,15,Fback voters.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
