PN,31109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778767870
OL,3,CWill Rayner take the chance to seize
OL,4,CLabour leadership? She's not ruling it
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FShe talked about taxing energy
OL,8,Fcompanies more in order to help people
OL,9,Fwith the cost-of-living crisis.
OL,11,FShe criticised the government's
OL,12,Fimmigration policy, saying it was too
OL,13,Ftough on those who've already arrived
OL,14,Fhere.
OL,16,FAnd she argued that Labour needs to
OL,17,Frediscover what it actually stands for
OL,18,Fand reconnect with its heartlands.
OL,20,FBut again, there is a hint of her own
OL,21,Fambition in her vision.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
