PN,31110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1778767870
OL,3,CWill Rayner take the chance to seize
OL,4,CLabour leadership? She's not ruling it
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,F"It's about who can deliver," she said.
OL,9,F"Who can deliver?" I asked. "Maybe
OL,10,Fthat suggests you don't think Keir
OL,11,FStarmer is the person to deliver?"
OL,13,F"Well, look, he's clearly setting
OL,14,Fout... He's set out the King's Speech".
OL,16,FHmm, hardly effusive support for Sir
OL,17,FKeir Starmer.
OL,19,FI still think Angela Rayner believes,
OL,20,Fin the depths of her heart, that she
OL,21,Fcould do better.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
